same path and where we started

00:48:27.410 --> 00:48:30.840
and where we're going
is exactly the same.

00:48:30.840 --> 00:48:34.600
There may be some people that
don't believe that, but it is so.

00:48:35.720 --> 00:48:41.280
And so we can effect a change

00:48:41.280 --> 00:48:46.030
that can cause catastrophic
things or repair.

00:48:46.030 --> 00:48:51.300
We share this world with all these
other creatures and they don't have

00:48:51.300 --> 00:48:52.750
that advantage, they just have

00:48:52.750 --> 00:48:56.730
to live here they don't
get to make the changes.

00:48:56.730 --> 00:49:00.310
And the clock is ticking
on that in a very big way.

00:49:00.310 --> 00:49:04.440
But ultimately the thought I
would like to leave you with is

00:49:04.440 --> 00:49:12.390 position:56%
as we struggle together in this very
important job of survival be kind.

00:49:12.390 --> 00:49:15.510
Thank you.

